SUMMARY:Second Annual Windsor Match Game
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a fun-filled evening in the historic sanctuary as we raise funds for our community outreach programs and ongoing maintenance for our 1898 building. Match wits and fill in the blanks with local Windsor “celebrities” including \nMichael LeComte\, Owner of Oak Tree Winery & Co-Owner of Tasting Notes\nand a special early-bird visit from a special North Pole guest\, Windsor Santa. \nGet ready for a night of laughter\, friendly competition\, and prizes. Don’t miss out on this opportunity to support our church and the whole Windsor community while having a great time and maybe earning a little money yourself. See you there!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/second-annual-windsor-match-game/
