SUMMARY:Fleetwood Macramé at the California Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Dance and sing along to Fleetwood Mac’s greatest hits!\nFleetwood Macramé has become one of the Bay Area’s most exciting tribute bands. What began as a simple exercise in fun has turned into an awe inspiring live experience complete with show stopping renditions of Fleetwood Mac’s greatest hits. Audience participation is encouraged\, and Bay Area crowds are coming in droves to sing along with Fleetwood Macramé. What’s more\, they sound so much like Fleetwood Mac\, if you closed your eyes\, you would think it was the real thing. Only it’s better\, because you are in the front row!\nThis event uses Zoned Seating:\nSeats within each zone are first-come-first-served. Ushers will seat you within your chosen zone upon arrival. (Zone C does not guarantee a seat.)\nCheck ticket descriptions for details\, & scroll down for a general zone chart.\nDance Floor Zonal Seating. Zone C- $25 (does not guarantee seating)\, Zone B $30\, Zone A $35. Day of show – $35 (C only – seating not guaranteed). \nwww.fleetwoodmacrame.com\nhttps://www.facebook.com/fleetwoodmacrame/\nTweets by fleetwoodmacra
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/fleetwood-macrame-at-the-california-theatre/
LOCATION:The California Theatre of Santa Rosa\, 528 7th Street\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golocal.coop/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Fleetwood.jpg
GEO:38.44252;-122.71621
