SUMMARY:Head Over Heels at 6th Street Playhouse
DESCRIPTION:A Kingdom at Risk\, a Beat That Won’t Quit\, and Love That Rules All!\n“It’s a feel good riot from start to finish.“\n— Jay Darcy\, Mancunion Media Group \nGet ready for a wild\, laugh-out-loud adventure with HEAD OVER HEELS—the electrifying musical comedy from the creative forces behind Hedwig and the Angry Inch\, Avenue Q\, and Spring Awakening! Nominated for Outstanding New Broadway Musical in 2019 and powered by the chart-topping hits of the legendary all-female rock band The Go-Go’s\, this high-energy show features beloved anthems like “We Got the Beat\,” “Our Lips Are Sealed\,” “Vacation\,” “Heaven is a Place on Earth\,” and “Mad About You.” \nJoin a spirited royal family on a whirlwind quest to save their kingdom from doom—only to realize that the key to their future isn’t written in fate\, but in their own hearts. Packed with irresistible music\, over-the-top comedy\, and a whole lot of love\, HEAD OVER HEELS is a dazzling\, feel-good spectacle that will have you dancing in your seat! \nContent Note: Head over Heels contains inferred strong language\, crude sexual references\, and adult themes. As such\, it is not recommended for patrons under the age of 13. \n 
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/head-over-heels-at-6th-street-playhouse-3/
LOCATION:6th Street Playhouse G.K. Hardt Theatre\, 52 West 6th Street\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Theater
GEO:38.4376841;-122.7235038
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=6th Street Playhouse G.K. Hardt Theatre 52 West 6th Street Santa Rosa CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=52 West 6th Street:geo:-122.7235038,38.4376841
END:VEVENT
