SUMMARY:Glory Dayz feat. Frankie Adel of Sha Na Na-Live Rock n' Roll!
DESCRIPTION:Get ready to rock n’ roll all night with Glory Dayz in Downtown Santa Rosa!\nJoin us for an unforgettable night at Glory Dayz feat. Frankie Adel of Sha Na Na – Live Rock n’ Roll in Downtown Santa Rosa! Get ready to rock out at Barrel Proof Lounge with the legendary Frankie Adel. It’s going to be a night filled with classic tunes\, high energy\, and good vibes. Don’t miss out on this epic event!\nGlory Dayz celebrates the best of the best classic rock-n-roll music from the 60’s through the 2000’s. With front man Frankie Adel – former lead singer from Sha Na Na – bringing his dynamic stage presence\, this band will keep you dancing all night long. Our collective experience includes working with some of music’s greats such as: Celine Dion\, Hall & Oates\, Huey Lewis\, Beach Boys\, Paul Anka\, Kenny Rogers and more. Our goal is to ignite music memories from your own Glory Days. We fill the house with good vibes\, good crowds and rockin-good times!\n21+\nDoors@7 / Show@8\n$10adv / $15door\nCheck out www.BarrelProofLounge.com for all sorts of good times ahead!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/glory-dayz-feat-frankie-adel-of-sha-na-na-live-rock-n-roll/
LOCATION:Barrel Proof Lounge\, 501 Mendocino Avenue\, Santa Rosa\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.44260;-122.71573
