SUMMARY:SCCC presents: Family Arts
DESCRIPTION:Family Silk Hoop Painting \nSilk painting with resist uses a barrier (resist) to block liquid dyes\, creating distinct\, sharp color areas like a stained-glass window. Artists outline designs with gutta resists\, which dry to form a waterproof fence\, allowing dyes to be applied and contained within sections\, and to mix with other silk dyes- the colors to create beautiful magical silk hoop paintings. \nBring out your inner artist in this fun workshop and create a piece of art of your! It’s also a perfect gift for upcoming Mother’s Day!
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/sccc-presents-family-arts/
LOCATION:Sebastopol Community Cultural Center\, 390 Morris St\, Sebastopol\, CA
CATEGORIES:Art,Kids and Family
GEO:38.4084;-122.82
