SUMMARY:April in Carneros
DESCRIPTION:Hospitality de Los Carneros is thrilled to announce the return of April in Carneros! \nChoose from 10 amazing wineries and their gorgeous locations to celebrate all that springtime has to offer. \nEnjoy a different and unique experience at each of the wineries including specials on wine and merchandise\, locally made food bites\, live music\, and more! All general admission ticket holders will receive a beautiful commemorative glass. Limit one per guest. \nTicket Options: \n$55 general admission \n$15 designated drivers \nYour ticket gets you access to the special event offerings at any (or all!) of the following wineries \nCarboniste Modern Sparkling Wine • Ceja Vineyards • Homewood Winery • Honrama Cellars • Meadowcroft Wines • Ricci Vineyards • Robledo Family Winery • Roche Winery and Vineyards • Talisman Wine • Ty Caton Vineyards \nDue to limited parking at some locations we are delighted to offer one FREE shuttle to help you visit wineries without the stress of parking. Please note this shuttle is limited to 14 seats. If you plan to use the shuttle the main parking sites to leave your cars are Carboniste and Meadowcroft. Schedule coming soon! \nPlease complete the survey during checkout to identify which winery you will be starting at to help us best prepare for your visit. \nURL: \nTickets: https://go.evvnt.com/3534074-0?pid=5514 \nPrice: General Admission: USD 55.00 \nCategory: Community \nDate and Time: 12 Apr 2026\, 11:00 AM – 4:00 PM \nVenue Details: 21684 8th St E\, 21684 8th Street East\, Sonoma\, California\, 95476\, United States
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/april-in-carneros/
LOCATION:21684 8th St E\, 21684 8th Street East\, Sonoma\, 95476
CATEGORIES:Music,Other
END:VEVENT
